            </h2>
            <div id="faq8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes, you can schedule a pickup and delivery time at your convenience.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 9 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq9">
                    What happens if my shipment gets delayed?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="faq9" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    We try to deliver on time, but delays due to traffic or weather can happen. We will notify you if any delay occurs.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 10 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
